Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is how I automated my morning routine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.72,0:00:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,all of it runs while I am still hitting snooze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.79,0:00:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,First, a script pulls my calendar and to-do list
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,then it picks the three things that actually matter today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It fires off a smart-plug command
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so my coffee starts brewing five minutes before I even walk into the kitchen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it records a 30-second voice note summarizing my day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.77,0:00:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and sends it to my own messaging app
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Three small automations
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That is it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.87,0:00:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But it saves me 20 minutes every single morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.03,0:00:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to wake up already behind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.86,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I wake up caught up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole thing is a 40-line script
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I will link it in the comments if you want to try it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.59,0:00:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously go automate one thing this weekend
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.49,0:01:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Future you will be annoyed you did not do it sooner
